metadata.name: Closure
metadata.description:
Codex Fantasia - Page 1

Closure

Don’t you see, it has been too late
Now that i know it won’t be far fetched
To think that I’ve never done no wrong
Just to get along

After every pieces has fallen
I know my head had swollen
And now the ropes has loosened 
I’ve finally noticed some cracks in the pavement

But I just wanna lay down
Flipping through Codex Fantasia on my own
Forget the broken branches and move on
